  ARTIFICIAL INTELLIGENCE & MACHINE LEARNING
============================================================

Concept:     Hallucination
Category:    Problem
Definition:  LLM confidently generates plausible but incorrect information
Year:        2020
Researchers: Many researchers
Applications:AI reliability, factual QA systems
Related:     Retrieval augmentation, grounding, calibration

Concept:     Fine-tuning
Category:    Training technique
Definition:  Updates pre-trained model weights on task-specific data
Year:        2018
Researchers: Howard/Ruder (ULMFiT)
Applications:Customizing LLMs, domain adaptation
Related:     Supervised fine-tuning, PEFT, LoRA

Concept:     LSTM
Category:    Architecture
Definition:  Gating mechanisms solve vanishing gradient in sequences
Year:        1997
Researchers: Hochreiter/Schmidhuber
Applications:NLP, speech, time series
Related:     GRU, RNN, gates, cell state

